These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, drama, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, blue, brown
House: colonial, ranch-style, victorian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, december, january
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, marigold
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, canasta
 1. the person playing canasta is the ranch-style house##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the colonial house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 5. the ranch-style house is the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | satire | superhero        | drama |
| Color          | brown    | blue        | pink    |
| House   | victorian        | colonial        | ranch-style    |
| Birthday           | january        | july    | december   |
| Flower         | daffodil    | marigold | dahlia |
| Game     | backgammon     | domino          | canasta     |

