.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, cola
City: liverpool, london, colone
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, rat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher, aristoff
3 different games are played: go, chess, canasta
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, pumpkin
1. the person traveling to liverpool is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating kale##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Beverage         | cola    | hot-chocolate     | almond-milk            |
| City           | london | liverpool | colone |
| Pet   | turtle    | rabbit      | rat             |
| Cigar   | blend | aristoff     | swisher             |
| Game         | chess  | canasta       | go           |
| Food     | pumpkin     | kale   | blueberry            |

