2. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
3. the fan of d&b is the person drinking juice##1
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the fan of dubstep is the person playing canasta##1
7. the fan of disco is the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
9. the victorian house is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Birthday         | september  | november     | october    |
| Sport           | basketball | biathlon  | snowboarding |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | juice | mirinda      |
