The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, bike, tram
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, gardening, video-games
 1. the art-deco house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the palace house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the palace house is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the owner of the pony is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Color      | lavender    | emerald     | aquamarine         |
| Birthday          | july  | december    | february         |
| House           | cottage | art-deco | palace          |
| Pet   | pony    | bird      | frog        |
| Transport   | tram     | roller     | bike          |
| Hobby         | video-games    | drawing | gardening |

