.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: go, canasta, scrabble
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy, sports
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, april
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, water
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, green
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, coach, videographer
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
2. the videographer is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the coach is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Game          | canasta          | scrabble      | go      |
| Movie-Genre         | sports        | comedy | zombie      |
| Birthday   | november          | january        | april       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | coffee   | water      |
| Color           | turquise           | green      | ivory         |
| Job         | videographer | project-manager    | coach |

 